import React from 'react'


const CreateSuperpowers = ({show, ohHide}) => {
    return (
        <Modal 
        show={show} 
        onHide={onHide}>
        <Modal.Header closeButton>
          <Modal.Title>ADD Nickname Hero</Modal.Title>
        </Modal.Header>
        <Modal.Body>
            <Form>
                <Form.Control 
                placeholder={"Lead the hero's real name"}
                />
            </Form>
        </Modal.Body>
        <Modal.Footer>
          <Button variant="outline-danger" onClick={onHide}>
            Close
          </Button>
          <Button variant="outline-success" onClick={onHide}>
            Save Changes
          </Button>
        </Modal.Footer>
      </Modal>
    )
}

export default CreateSuperpowers
